Uses of ExecutionContext in org.mindswap.owls.process.execution
 

Classes in org.mindswap.owls.process.execution with type parameters of type ExecutionContext
 interface ExecutionSupport<C extends ExecutionContext>
          This interface specifies the methods that need to be implemented for supporting execution of all control constructs specified by OWL-S as well as execution of all process types.
 

Classes in org.mindswap.owls.process.execution that implement ExecutionContext
 class BaseExecutionContext
          This class stores the (current) values of process variables in the scope of a process instance that is currently being executed.
